  description="Decanter vs disc centrifuge compared: G-force, particle size, solids capacity, design, and maintenance differences. Expert selection guide from Dolphin."
  heroImage="/images/difference-between-decanter-centrifuge-disc-centrifuge/disc-centrifuge-alfa-laval-whpx-510-300.webp"
